        >Email</a
      > or --> Just drop me a DM on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hananurrehman/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">LinkedIn</a>. 
      Otherwise I can be also be found sharing wisdom on <a href="https://club.ministryoftesting.com/" class="text-indigo-600 underline">Ministry of testing</a>.
      I'll be delighted to help you out.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
